'''Alto''' is an [[Unincorporated area|unincorporated community]] in [[Richland Parish, Louisiana|Richland Parish]], [[Louisiana]], [[United States]].<ref>{{GNIS|532147}}</ref>

==History==
Alto was likely named from its lofty elevation.<ref>{{cite book|last=Leeper|first=Clare D'Artois|title=Louisiana Place Names: Popular, Unusual, and Forgotten Stories of Towns, Cities, Plantations, Bayous, and Even Some Cemeteries|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ZHeeUa0xNxcC&pg=PA15|date=19 October 2012|publisher=LSU Press|isbn=978-0-8071-4740-5|page=15}}</ref>

